data.description: Welcome to this charming Monterey plan 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home at Windbrooke at Carriage Trails, recently built in 2022, located on the largest corner lot in the community. Inside, the home offers a comfortable and open layout with LVP flooring and designer upgrades throughout, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen is a highlight, granite countertops, large walk in pantry, stainless steel appliances and spacious  dining area, perfect for daily entertaining, painted concrete patio is accessible from the kitchen perfect for warm weather gatherings. Large windows bring in plenty of natural light, creating a pleasant connection between the indoors and the outside. You'll love working from home with the French door study. Huge loft located on the second floor provides an excellent opportunity for upstairs living area. The primary bedroom has a stunning vaulted ceiling and oversized walk-in closet. Owner's will enjoy a soaking tub and a walk in shower. Additional bedrooms with walk in closet. Spacious laundry room located on the second floor. The unfinished basement, already equipped with rough-in for a full bath, offers potential for future expansion to suit your needs. This home also includes a 2-car garage with storage. Fully fenced yard. No need to build when you could own this gorgeous colonial home.
